column2: SELECT up_id,  dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) as objId   FROM #upload  WHERE  dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) IS NOT NULL  SELECT TOP #   p.ra,p.dec, cast(str(p.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,cast(str(p.[dec],#,#) as float) as dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,ISNULL(s.z,#) as redshift,ISNULL(s.z_noqso,#) as z_noqso,ISNULL(s.z_person,#) as z_person,ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as redshiftErr  FROM ..PhotoObj AS p  LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  ( p.type = # OR p.type = #)   ORDER BY x.up_id
